ps://www.theverge.com/2023/10/3/23901448/discovery-plus-price-increase-monthly-cost&quot;>;Discovery Plus&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.theverge.com/2023/8/9/23826500/disney-plus-hulu-no-ads-plan-price-increases&quot;>;Disney Plus&lt;/a>; 只是最近的几个例子，但仍有方法以应对价格上涨。毕竟，黑色星期五带来了各种各样的优惠，包括节省每月流媒体账单的方法。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;VJkz6i&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的 2023 年黑色星期五最佳科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971107/black-friday-2023-best-deals- tech-earbuds-gaming-tablets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best -ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;7hzi4e&quot;>;事实上，一些流媒体服务正在提供抵消近期价格上涨的优惠 —好吧，至少暂时如此。例如，Paramount Plus 可能&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/22/23733505/paramount-plus-showtime-price-increase&quot;>;将其最便宜计划的价格提高到每月 5.99 美元&lt;/a>;，但目前起价仅为 1.99 美元。更好的是，新订阅者和回访订阅者都有资格享受这笔交易，这是真正的罕见......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black- friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965708/black-friday-2023-streaming-deals-max-paramount-plus-hulu-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>